::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501031604: Config/Level/Mission/5010316/Act/Act501031604.json-->
::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' Groo~ Groo groo!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501031604_62-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031604_62-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell a dad joke.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031638-->
:::This is your strong suit! You took the grand prize in the Astral Express dad joke contest you made up in your mind!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501031604_65-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031604_65-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell a joke about work.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031640-->
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' Why did the bear get fired?
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' ...
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' ...Because it always skipped work in the winter!
::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' ...Groo?
::::You realize you told the worst joke ever. Clearly arctic bears don't hibernate in the winter.
::::...Better luck next time.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell a joke about a ball.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031647-->
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' What kind of ball doesn't bounce?
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' ...
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' ...A snowball!
::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' ...Groo?
::::...What about iron balls? Or steel balls? Or osmium alloy balls?
::::Terrible... This is not the kind of joke someone of your talent should be telling.
::::...Better luck next time.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell a joke about snowmen.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031655-->
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' How should you greet an old snowman?
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' ...
::::'''(Trailblazer):''' ...Hello, Mr. Water!
::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' ...Groo?
::::...Dang, no reaction. This was clearly one of your proudest dad jokes... It seems that the arctic bear is a species with high standards when it comes to dad jokes. This is a tough crowd.
::::...Better luck next time.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Return}} Let's do something else.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501031604_62-->
:::;(<!--Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString)-->)
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Sing a lullaby.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031663-->
:::::'''(Trailblazer):''' Ahem... Ahem!
:::::You cleared your throat... It's your time to shine!
:::::'''(Trailblazer):''' Cough... Cough cough!
:::::Oh no! Your throat isn't feeling great today... Better take a lozenge!
:::::A refreshing mint flavor bursts from the back of your tongue, moistening your throat and vocal cords... That feels great, no wonder Welt's always gobbling sweets! Now, you are ready.
:::::'''(Trailblazer):''' Ah... Ahem!
:::::...Dang, how does that lullaby start again?
:::::It's right on the tip of your tongue... An adult should know how to be flexible, so you give up the futile struggles &mdash; just take out your phone and check.
:::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' Zzz... Zzz...
:::::As you were wrapped up in all this, the little cub fell asleep.
:::::That's fine. You should save your wonderful singing voice for someone who really wants to hear it anyway!
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Feed it something.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031675-->
:::::You pull a large hazelnut from your pocket, it looks delicious...
:::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' ...Groo! Groohoo!
:::::...Why did you have a hazelnut in your pocket? That's not important, it's already in your hand now.
:::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Toss the hazelnut to the cub.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501031679-->
:::::The hazelnut soars through the air in a graceful arc.
:::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' ...Arf! Groo!
:::::'''Plains Bear Cub:''' Groo... Hoo... Arf!
:::::The cub cries out with happiness. If there were such a thing as a friendship level, that would have scored you some great points.
